B.Og=new A.a1("B738/M in the flight plan means Boeing 737-800 with Medium wake turbulence category.","U\xe7u\u015f plan\u0131ndaki B738/M, Boeing 737-800 ve Orta a\u011f\u0131rl\u0131k kategorisi anlam\u0131na gelir.","/M")
B.Qc=new A.a1("EET/LTAA0123 means the estimated elapsed time to the LTAA FIR boundary is 1 hour 23 minutes.","EET/LTAA0123, LTAA FIR s\u0131n\u0131r\u0131na tahmini ge\xe7i\u015f s\xfcresinin 1 saat 23 dakika oldu\u011fu anlam\u0131na gelir.","EET")
