B.W3=new A.m(B.v,"\ud83d\udccb CRAFT Format\u0131",'IFR clearance\'\u0131 hat\u0131rlamak i\xe7in **CRAFT** k\u0131saltmas\u0131 kullan\u0131l\u0131r:\n\n**C** \u2192 **Clearance limit** (hedef havaliman\u0131 veya fix)\n**R** \u2192 **Route** (rota \u2014 SID + airways + STAR)\n**A** \u2192 **Altitude** (ba\u015flang\u0131\xe7 y\xfcksekli\u011fi / FL)\n**F** \u2192 **Frequency** (ilk frekans)\n**T** \u2192 **Transponder code** (squawk)\n\n**Yayg\u0131n ifadeler:**\n\u2022 "Cleared to [destination] via [route]" \u2192 rotay\u0131 ver\n\u2022 "Climb via SID" \u2192 SID ile t\u0131rman (irtifa k\u0131s\u0131tlamalar\u0131 dahil)\n\u2022 "Expect [FL] ten minutes after departure" \u2192 kalk\u0131\u015ftan 10 dk sonra [FL] bekle\n\u2022 "Departure frequency [xxx.x]" \u2192 kalk\u0131\u015f frekans\u0131\n\u2022 "Readback correct" \u2192 geri okuma do\u011fru',null,null,null)
B.Oj=new A.a1('"Turkish 234, cleared to London Heathrow via KEMAL3A departure, then airways L602, Upper Blue 2, expect flight level 370 ten minutes after departure, departure frequency 119.1, squawk 2374."',"C=Heathrow, R=KEMAL3A+L602+UB2, A=ba\u015flang\u0131\xe7 SID, bekle FL370, F=119.1, T=2374","cleared to \u2026 via \u2026 expect \u2026 departure frequency \u2026 squawk")
