B.YO=new A.m(B.ap,"\u2708\ufe0f Tamamlama Sorular\u0131 i\xe7in S\u0131nav Stratejisi",'1. **T\xfcmceyi ba\u015ftan sona** oku \u2014 havac\u0131l\u0131k durumunu anla\n2. **Dilbilgisel bo\u015flu\u011fu** belirle \u2014 isim mi? fiil mi? s\u0131fat m\u0131? edat m\u0131?\n3. **\xd6bekleri** kontrol et \u2014 "declare an emergency" (acil durum ilan etmek), "announce" de\u011fil\n4. Havac\u0131l\u0131\u011fa \xf6zg\xfc \xf6bekler:\n   \u2022 declare **an emergency** / mayday\n   \u2022 squawk **a code** (7700)\n   \u2022 divert **to** an alternate\n   \u2022 request **immediate** / priority assistance',null,null,null)
