B.Qb=new A.a1("E) RWY 06/24 CLSD DUE RESURFACING WIP. EXPECT DUST AND DEBRIS IN VICINITY.","Pist 06/24 y\xfczey yenileme \xe7al\u0131\u015fmas\u0131 nedeniyle kapal\u0131. \xc7evrede toz ve moloz bekleniyor.","CLSD DUE RESURFACING WIP")
