B.a_E=new A.m(B.x,"Neden standart ifadeler \xf6nemlidir","Kabin g\xfcvenlik anonslar\u0131 **d\xfczenleyici kurumlar taraf\u0131ndan onaylanm\u0131\u015f** sabit ifadeler i\xe7erir. IATA ve havayollar\u0131n\u0131n kendi prosed\xfcrleri, yolcular\u0131n her u\xe7u\u015fta ayn\u0131 mesaj\u0131 anlamas\u0131n\u0131 sa\u011flamak i\xe7in belirli kelimeler kullan\u0131r.\n\nBu kal\u0131plar\u0131 ezberlemek, bask\u0131 alt\u0131nda bile do\u011fru ve net ileti\u015fim kurman\u0131z\u0131 sa\u011flar.",null,null,null)
